Directed by A.R. Mohan

Written by A.R. Mohan

Cast Anandhi (Lachimi). Keshav Deepak (Actor). Vennela Kishore (English Teacher). Allari Naresh (Sripada Srinivas). Praveen (VRO Assistant). Sampath Raj (Collector).

Languages Telugu

Producers Balaji Gutta.

Production Hasya Movies. Zee Studios.
